text: Hi Nur, thank you so much for your kind message!! I really send all my best to you in such a difficult time, I hope soon we can have some certainty to the situation we've been put in. I hope you are staying safe and healthy too :-) !!

Great to know you are fine, Rebecca.
I hope you can make your time at home enjoyable. Here is a link for you to listen which I believe you may be interested.
<https://www.accessvfx.org/podcast>

Please do not hesitate to ask your questions on these days too. I will be happy to assist.

Stay safe and healthy!
